NK101(de)001:1: // a pa ka r+sha s+ya d+h+wa dza badz+ra sa t+wa
NK101(de)001:2: ma h+aa na b+ha m+au la ta n+t+ra n+aa ma
NK101(de)001:3: sti sma /// mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan rdo rje
NK101(de)001:4: sems dpa' nam mkha' che rtsab'i rgyud ces bya ba
NK101(de)001:5: sti sma /// bzhugs / rgya gar skad du /
NK101(de)001:6: badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ma h+aa kar+sha k+aa ri ka /
NK101(de)001:8: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)001:9: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK101(de)001:11: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK101(de)001:12: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK101(de)001:13: rnam dag lam chen kun grol phyir //
NK101(de)001:14: ma skye mi 'gag cir mi dgongs //
NK101(de)001:15: byams pas don ni rnam sbyangs phyir //
NK101(de)001:16: snying rje chen po cir mi mdzad //
NK101(de)001:17: che bas che ba zab mo yi //
NK101(de)001:18: yon tan cir yang sngags pa med //
NK101(de)001:19: don rnams ji bzhin mi bskyod de //
NK101(de)001:20: bya ba med pas grol ba'ang grol //
NK101(de)001:21: rang byung ye shes brtsal med pas //
NK101(de)001:22: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK101(de)001:24: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:26: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)001:27: phyin ci log tu rnam brtags kyang //
NK101(de)001:28: grol ba rang byung gzhan las min //
NK101(de)001:29: rang bzhin gyis che ba la gnas pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:30: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' ba //
NK101(de)001:31: shes rab thabs la brten pas 'grub //
NK101(de)001:32: ming tsam gzhan la brten 'dra yang //
NK101(de)001:33: mngon sum bde ba rang las 'byung //
NK101(de)001:34: brtsal ba dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:35: cho 'phrul chen po dka' ba min //
NK101(de)001:36: yon tan kun ldan stobs kyi rnams //
NK101(de)001:37: ji bzhin rtogs pa phra ba yis //
NK101(de)001:38: de ma thag tu rang las 'byung //
NK101(de)001:39: snang ba med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK101(de)001:40: ma brtsal bzhag na sgom pa yin //
NK101(de)001:41: de dang der ni rnam brtsal na //
NK101(de)001:42: de las de bzhin de mi 'byung //
NK101(de)001:43: brjod pa dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:44: mchog tu gsang ba'i chos nyid ni //
NK101(de)001:45: rna dbang gzhan las thos mi 'gyur //
NK101(de)001:46: de bzhin lce yi dbang pos kyang //
NK101(de)001:47: de la brjod du rdul tsam med //
NK101(de)001:49: 'gro ba las kyis mi 'khor ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:50: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal byang chub sems //
NK101(de)001:51: kun tu chub pa rnam par rol //
NK101(de)001:52: de la bskyod pa med bzhin du //
NK101(de)001:53: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar mnyam par gnas //
NK101(de)001:54: khyad par cir yang mtshungs pa la //
NK101(de)001:55: las so zhes ni rnam par brtags //
NK101(de)001:56: ci ste las kyis dbang 'gyur na //
NK101(de)001:57: rang byung ye shes yod ma yin //
NK101(de)001:58: rgyu nyid rdo rje rkyen dang 'dra //
NK101(de)001:59: ma skyes pas na 'jig pa med //
NK101(de)001:60: gdod nas snying po byang chub la //
NK101(de)001:61: brtsam pa'i bsam pas dbyings mi bskyod //
NK101(de)001:62: rtsal sems dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:63: yon tan chen po'i bsam gtan ni //
NK101(de)001:64: bsam gtan nyid pas bsam du med //
NK101(de)001:65: ma bsams ma sbyangs chos bzhin du //
NK101(de)001:66: rnam rtog nyid las ye shes skye //
NK101(de)001:67: phra ba'i sgo mor ming btags shing //
NK101(de)001:68: sems kyi dben pa'i lam 'tshol zhing //
NK101(de)001:69: dgon pa'i rgyud du dben 'dzin na //
NK101(de)001:70: brtags na rnam par rtog 'gyur sgom //
NK101(de)001:71: rgyu dang 'bras bur ming btags nas //
NK101(de)001:72: dge sdig gnyis ka rnam par sel //
NK101(de)001:74: blang dor brod pa mchog tu skyed //
NK101(de)001:75: gnyis su med pa skyon dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:76: chags dang ma chags tshig gi lam //
NK101(de)001:77: dbu ma bzhin te brag cha 'dra //
NK101(de)001:78: bde dang sdug bsngal rgyu mthun zhes //
NK101(de)001:79: 'gro ba'i mgon po sems dpas gsungs //
NK101(de)001:80: ye shes rang las 'byung ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:81: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang //
NK101(de)001:82: byang chub chen po'i lam las 'byung //
NK101(de)001:83: kun spyod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK101(de)001:84: chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan zhes gsungs //
NK101(de)001:85: nam mkha'i rtog pa skye med cing //
NK101(de)001:86: rtog pa de nyid nam mkha' 'dra //
NK101(de)001:87: mi chags nam mkha'i dngos po la //
NK101(de)001:88: rang don chen po nam mkha' 'byung //
NK101(de)001:89: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le /
NK101(de)001:90: gzungs kyi sbyor thabs kyi skabs /
NK101(de)001:91: rtog med mnyam nyid chos kyi sku //
NK101(de)001:92: bzung bas mi zin chu zla 'dra //
NK101(de)001:93: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa yin //
NK101(de)001:94: a li k+aa li zab tu bstan //
NK101(de)001:95: 'di ni a dang mdzes pa'i ta //
NK101(de)001:96: pa dang yan lag spros pa bzhin //
NK101(de)001:97: 'jig rten yongs kyi spyod yul la //
NK101(de)001:98: sangs rgyas gsung gi zab mo 'byung //
NK101(de)001:99: e ma sangs rgyas spyod yul 'di //
NK101(de)001:100: btsal bas rnyed pa'i gnas med de //
NK101(de)001:101: drug gi chos bzhin yul med pas //
NK101(de)001:102: mdongs pas nam mkha' bsnyams pa bzhin //
NK101(de)001:103: gong nas gong du tshangs pa'i las //
NK101(de)001:104: bya bral chos dang mthun pa med //
NK101(de)001:105: ci ste lam la bgrod gyur na //
NK101(de)001:106: nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin thug pa med //
NK101(de)001:108: de ltar de bzhin de yi phyir //
NK101(de)001:109: de la de bstan de yang thob //
NK101(de)001:110: de ni snying po de bas na //
NK101(de)001:111: de las de 'byung ngo mtshar che //
NK101(de)001:112: sngon gyi de dang da ltar de //
NK101(de)001:113: de bzhin de yi gnas su che //
NK101(de)001:114: de ltar de yi lam 'dra ba //
NK101(de)001:115: de ni de yi rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)001:116: de dang 'dra ba yongs kyi lam //
NK101(de)001:117: zla ba las byung rten dang bcas //
NK101(de)001:118: kun gyi mnyam nyid yin pa la //
NK101(de)001:119: phyogs su bltas pas 'grub pa med //
NK101(de)001:120: chags pa dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:121: da lta'i bde dang phyi ma'i bde //
NK101(de)001:122: mngon sum pa dang rgyab nas 'byung //
NK101(de)001:123: de yang rnam pa'i skyon yin pas //
NK101(de)001:124: de la brten par mi bya'o //
NK101(de)001:125: gdod ma nas che ba snying po nyid kyi skabs /
NK101(de)001:126: dus gsum gcig ste khyab par med //
NK101(de)001:127: sngon med phyis med gdod nas 'byung //
NK101(de)001:128: chos skus khyab par gcig pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)001:129: che ba'i chen por rang bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)001:130: kun tu smon lam dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:131: srid pa gsum na sbyong ba yang //
NK101(de)001:132: ming tsam sgyu mar snang ba ste //
NK101(de)001:133: 'khor los sgyur ba'i gnas chen yang //
NK101(de)001:134: sgyu mar sbyong ba'i bsti gnas yin //
NK101(de)001:135: rnam dpyod dus la ltos pa rnams //
NK101(de)001:137: ma bral smon pa spyod pas na //
NK101(de)001:138: stong po'i mtshan nyid gsungs pa bzhin //
NK101(de)001:140: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK101(de)001:141: rnal 'byor nam mkha'i bya lam gnas //
NK101(de)001:142: ma byung ma skyes snying po la /
NK101(de)001:143: sgro btags chos kun ga la yod //
NK101(de)001:144: phyi nang gnyis ka phyi nyid nang //
NK101(de)001:145: zab mo cha shas rtog yul med //
NK101(de)001:146: srid pa ming tsam log pa'i stobs //
NK101(de)001:147: de bas ting 'dzin mnyam dang bral //
NK101(de)001:148: de la tha tshig phyi dang nang //
NK101(de)001:149: rang bzhin phung po khams bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)001:151: tha tshig ming du btags pa med //
NK101(de)001:152: ye shes chen po'i thig le /
NK101(de)001:154: mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgya //
NK101(de)001:155: mi bskyod pa ni ye shes te //
NK101(de)001:156: mi len pas na bdag med cing //
NK101(de)001:157: mi 'dor tshig bral mnyam nyid do //
NK101(de)001:158: gang dang gang gis gang du yang //
NK101(de)001:159: kun 'khor kun spyod bdag las byung //
NK101(de)001:160: 'di la skyes pa bud med ces //
NK101(de)001:161: mnyam pa'i rgyal pos yongs ma gsungs //
NK101(de)001:162: dngos grub chen po'i bde ba la chags pa spong ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:163: 'di la brtul zhugs drag shul gyis //
NK101(de)001:164: gnas su bya ba'i ming med de //
NK101(de)001:165: a dang par ni rnam ldan na //
NK101(de)001:167: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges par //
NK101(de)001:168: ji ltar bltas pa de ltar snang //
NK101(de)001:169: snang 'dod rtsol sems bde ba yang //
NK101(de)001:170: de ni de sgrib skyon chen yin //
NK101(de)001:171: byang chub yan lag kun gyi sgo //
NK101(de)001:172: cha lugs sgom pa chu zla bzhin //
NK101(de)001:173: ma gos ma chags 'byung gyur kyang //
NK101(de)001:174: sgom pa byis pa'i spyod yul yin //
NK101(de)001:175: dkyil 'khor khro gnyer cha lugs kyis //
NK101(de)001:176: khro bdag chen po'i lus bzung nas //
NK101(de)001:177: yi ge mngon du phyung na yang //
NK101(de)001:178: zhi ba de nyid mthong ba med //
NK101(de)001:179: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yangs pas //
NK101(de)001:180: gang ltar spyad kyang me tog skye //
NK101(de)001:181: mtshan ma med pa'i dbang gis na //
NK101(de)001:183: rtsol ba dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:184: gleng bral 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK101(de)001:186: bdag dang gzhan don mi 'byed pas //
NK101(de)001:187: sgyu ma lhun grub yul la rol //
NK101(de)001:188: chos nyid kun tu mi 'gyur ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:189: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK101(de)001:190: 'gyur ba ma yin drang por gnas //
NK101(de)001:191: nam mkha' bzhin du mtha' mnyam zhing //
NK101(de)001:192: gzhan las ltos 'gyur chos ma yin //
NK101(de)001:193: lhun gyis gnas pas bde chen de //
NK101(de)001:194: mtshungs pa med pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK101(de)001:195: rang gi mthu yis rig pa las //
NK101(de)001:197: sla zhing dka' la dka' phyir sla //
NK101(de)001:198: mngon sum mi gnas kun la khyab //
NK101(de)001:199: ming tsam 'di zhes bstan pa ni //
NK101(de)001:200: rdo rje sems dpas mtshon du med //
NK101(de)001:201: rgyu rkyen las mi 'grub pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:202: ngo mtshar rmad byung rol pa 'di //
NK101(de)001:203: bya bral nam mkha' ji bzhin du //
NK101(de)001:204: cir yang mi dmigs gti mug las //
NK101(de)001:205: de ma thag tu rang las 'byung //
NK101(de)001:206: 'di ni thams cad mtshungs pa'i lam //
NK101(de)001:207: 'gro ba kun la rang zhin gnas //
NK101(de)001:208: byis pas bslad pas 'khrul ba'i phyir //
NK101(de)001:209: sman nyid sman pa 'tshol ba bzhin //
NK101(de)001:210: 'gro ba yongs la sangs rgyas par bstan pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:211: go ba'i yul na bde ba che //
NK101(de)001:215: ma des 'ja' tshon kha dog las //
NK101(de)001:216: rigs kyi khyad par mngon par snang //
NK101(de)001:217: de bzhin g.yo rdul mi g.yo ba //
NK101(de)001:218: 'byung ba lnga po gtso chen yin //
NK101(de)001:219: kun tu bzang po'i thig le /
NK101(de)001:222: tha snyad ming la mi gnas te //
NK101(de)001:223: skye 'gag med par rnam brtags shing //
NK101(de)001:224: de nyid dus gsum chen por sbyor //
NK101(de)001:225: mnyam pas rim par bkod pa med //
NK101(de)001:226: gcig pas phyogs su bsngo dang bral //
NK101(de)001:227: tshogs kyi rgyan rnams bkram pa yang //
NK101(de)001:228: rang bzhin gnas pas 'grib pa med //
NK101(de)001:229: lhun gyis grub pas mi bsngo zhing //
NK101(de)001:230: gdod nas dag pa bdud rtsi yin //
NK101(de)001:231: 'du mched bcu gnyis khyad par las //
NK101(de)001:232: lhag pa'i bsam pas bzung ba med //
NK101(de)001:233: rang bzhin gyis lhun gyis grub pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:234: yid kyi bsam pa yon bdag ste //
NK101(de)001:235: bltas pas tshogs ni bkram pa yin //
NK101(de)001:236: mthong bar gyur pas dngos grub la //
NK101(de)001:237: de nyid mnyam bzhag rdzogs pa'o //
NK101(de)001:239: yud tsam bzung bas sbyor ba yin //
NK101(de)001:240: dga' bar gyur pa dam tshig ste //
NK101(de)001:241: thabs kyi gar thabs bskyod pa yis //
NK101(de)001:242: gnyis med sbyor ba phul ba yin //
NK101(de)001:244: mi gzung gtong bas gtor ma yin //
NK101(de)001:245: bya ba med pa'i las rnams te //
NK101(de)001:246: mi rtog ye shes bgegs bsal nas //
NK101(de)001:247: mi gsungs mnyam nyid sngags tshig go //
NK101(de)001:248: bdag dang bcas pas gtor ma 'ching ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:249: bla ma mchod dang gtong ba dang //
NK101(de)001:250: de bzhin bsod nams thams cad kyang //
NK101(de)001:251: ma chags mi g.yo'i stobs med na //
NK101(de)001:253: lung 'grel ba ming tsam brdar bstan ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)001:254: de bas de lung de nyid las //
NK101(de)001:255: de la de byar sgrib par 'gyur //
NK101(de)001:256: de ltar de la de rtog na //
NK101(de)001:257: de la de nyid 'grub pa med //
NK101(de)001:258: lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le /
NK101(de)001:259: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK101(de)001:260: lung thams cad kyi bdag nyid dpal rdo rje sems
NK101(de)001:261: dpa'i zhal nas gsungs pa rdzogs so////'di la kun tu
NK101(de)001:262: bzang po'i thig le'i skabs gnyis par mthong ba med
NK101(de)001:264: nyon mongs pa yi dbang gis na //
NK101(de)001:265: ta la'i mgo bo bcad pa dang //
NK101(de)001:266: sa bon me yis bsregs pa dang //
NK101(de)001:267: de yi dbang du mi 'gyur ston //
NK101(de)001:268: de nas rnam grangs sogs gsungs te //
NK101(de)001:269: byang chub kyi sems las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang
